The user accesses the URL www.foobar.com, which is routed to HAProxy, a load balancer that distributes tasks by sending them to the web server and app server, protected by a firewall using the HTTPS protocol.

Both can access the codebase to execute the code logic while being protected by antivirus firewall.

With the need to continue up to the database for the database query.

And the client monitoring to oversee operation and availability.
